{"tid":472393,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"曾淵滄﹕買領展收息媲美買樓收租","createTime":"2017-11-18T07:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T07:43:26.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"efb0a01999c85b02205f732526c16cbef110abcf","tid":472393,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T07:43:26.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】領展（0823）前日公布業績，昨日股價破頂，再創歷史新高，領展同時有投資或投機價值，從投資的角度來看，買領展收股息，股息年年有增長，並不比買樓收租差，現在買樓按揭可借的比例很低，至少得投入數百萬現金才能買樓收租，買領展則多少隨意，很適合長期投資收息。從投機的角度來看，領展股價長期處於強勢，恒指在2007年見頂，至今10年過去仍未再創新高，而領展早已創出歷史新高，而且不斷地創新高，目前的股價已經比2007年高了許多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171110/s00004/1510250421572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171110%2Fs00004%2F1510250421572&d=iXPG7n%2BZlQYRPUdsVi1iJmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=e0db7e44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171110%2Fs00004%2F1510250421572&h=01621b76\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171110/s00004/1510250421572</a>"}]}